  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the fresh blackberries and pat them dry with a paper towel.",
    "In a blender, combine the blackberries, irish moss, coconut cream, honey, mint leaves, lemon juice, and vanilla powder.",
    "Blend the mixture on high speed until smooth and creamy.",
    "Taste and adjust the sweetness and flavor as needed.",
    "Spoon the mixture into the stone bowl dolsot.",
    "Place the stone bowl on the lazy susan spinner.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional fresh mint leaves and blackberries, if desired."
  ],
